  "title": "Delivery driver",
  "description": "<h1>Company Van Driver — Honest Crafters</h1>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore<br>\n <strong>Type:</strong> Full-time (Delivery / Driver role)<br>\n <strong>Apply (fastest):</strong> WhatsApp Jimmy at <strong>8323 2555</strong> </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join Honest Crafters — Singapore’s specialist in luxury leather restoration — as a Delivery Driver. You’ll be the friendly, reliable face who collects and returns customers’ treasured bags, shoes and other leather items. This is a hands-on role that combines safe driving, basic vehicle care and excellent customer service.</p>\n<h2>Key responsibilities</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Collect and deliver leather goods to/from customers and business partners on scheduled routes.</li>\n  <li>Safely drive the company van and perform basic daily vehicle checks (oil, tyres, lights, cleanliness).</li>\n  <li>Load, secure and unload leather items with care — these are high-value, delicate goods.</li>\n  <li>Handle cash collections and obtain customer signatures; ensure invoices and delivery paperwork are accurate and returned to the office.</li>\n  <li>Call or message customers to confirm appointments and ensure smooth handovers.</li>\n  <li>Report any vehicle faults, delivery issues or customer feedback to the Operations team promptly.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a neat, professional appearance and provide courteous customer service at all times.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid<strong> Class 3A</strong> driving licence (Singapore).</li>\n  <li>Proven safe driving record and ability to navigate Singapore roads.</li>\n  <li>Able to read and communicate in English for delivery notes and customer calls.</li>\n  <li>Reliable, punctual and able to work independently with minimal supervision.</li>\n  <li>Comfortable handling small, high-value items (bags, shoes). No heavy lifting required.</li>\n  <li>Basic cash-handling experience and trustworthiness for collecting payments.</li>\n  <li>Mobile phone for customer calls/WhatsApp and route coordination.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Perks &amp; practical notes</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Regular, consistent delivery routes (no heavy-item logistics).</li>\n  <li>Company van <strong>may be driven home</strong> after shift (subject to company policy).</li>\n  <li>Onboarding and on-the-job training — we’ll teach you how to handle and secure leather goods properly.</li>\n  <li>Supportive small-team environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’re punctual, careful with valuables and enjoy meeting customers, we want to meet you. <strong>WhatsApp Jimmy at 8323 2555</strong> with a short intro and your driving licence details.</p>",
